public class FinalProject
extends RobotGuiBase

The base final project class used for the Fall Semester, 2002. Provides a black path with 3 forks and a pushable barrel at the end of each fork. Also has a gray border, and a small gray box with a lightsource in it. Designed to allow demonstration of skills using iteration, selection, and the use of a touch, light, and differential-light sensor.
